prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style sloth wearing a tiny, lopsided party hat, clinging upside down to a colorful party streamer instead of a branch. The sloth has a wide, blissfully slow smile and is holding a single, unlit birthday candle in one paw. Floating gently around the sloth are a few soft, colorful watercolor splotches that look like out-of-focus confetti. Centered below the sloth, the words "happy birthday" are written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is a flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style, featuring soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the figures and splotches. The background is a clean, minimalist white.
